title: DDFP 157: Dynasties, fantasies & Bieber
itunes:title: DDFP 157: Dynasties, fantasies & Bieber
description:
Shek and Rank are joined by NFL.com's fantasy hall of famer Michael Fabiano to begin plotting 2013 fantasy draft strategies. The fellas also kibitz with Around The League scribe Dan Hanzus about a number of subjects on the newest Black List, including NBA dynasties and JaMarcus Russell's comeback attempt.
